# CLAUDE.local.md Template

Copy this file to `CLAUDE.local.md` for local settings (gitignored).

## Local Environment

```bash
# OpenRouter API key (or put it in ~/.creds/openrouter.env)
export OPENROUTER_API_KEY="sk-or-..."
# Optional overrides
export OPENROUTER_MODEL="google/gemini-2.5-flash-lite"

# Anthropic API key for Claude backend
export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY="sk-ant-..."

# Brave Search API key (for MCP server)
export BRAVE_API_KEY="..."
```

## Personal Preferences

